<br>
Druids, Necros, Shaman and Mages have been given spells that can sense and disarm traps on objects.  This is an obvious attempt to prevent groups from taking their tank, chanter, cleric teams and leaving the rest of us behind.  Although, I'm seeing that Chanters get a weaker, lower level version of this ability.<br>
<br>
Necros get one more Damage over Time spell, but this one seems to have emphasis on the damage and less on the time.<br>
<br>
Finally, Necros, Mages, and Beasties share a &quot;Protection&quot; line of spells that absorb damage.  Can't tell if it has a component yet.   <p>Sytox 63 Warlock<br>
<br>
An Arrow of Light Founder<br>
